* Tính từ mô tả hoặc cung cấp thêm thông tin về chủ ngữ. Tính từ thường theo sau một dạng của động từ to be (am, is, are).

A balloon is round.
Balls are round.
Jane is pretty.
I am thirsty.

[[[

I'm not hungry. I am thirsty.
You're not stupid. You are intelligent.
We aren't skimpy. We are generous.
They aren't sad. They are happy.
He's not short. He is tall.
She isn't mild. She is rude.
It's not lovely. It is ugly.
Ben and Jack are good-looking.

]]]